fields.title: Who We Are
fields.body: We are the Future Librarians of Virginia (FLVA). We want to help those looking to become librarians succeed with tools and insights from those of us who already have the expertise.

fields.title: Why You Should Join
fields.body:
When you join FLVA you'll be sure that you're in good hands. With plenty of experienced librarians (both young and old) in this communicative active group, you'll be able to ask any questions you have about becoming a librarian and we're ready to support you and help you through the process!

Joining our group is becoming part of a community that not only helps you along the way but also has your back.
